  "text": "4 An Example: The Above Threshold Algorithm Barthe, Gaboardi, Grégoire, Hsu, and Strub extended the logic apRHL to the logic apRHL+ with new proof rules to describe the sparse vector technique (see also [CITATION_1] Section 3.6] ). They gave a formal proof of the differential privacy of above threshold algorithm in the preprint [CITATION_2] in arXiv.",
